item.title: Gazoo - PMPVsAustralia
item.description: G"day Mate, how ya goin" ?It"s Sunday across most of the world, and I"m doing whatevz" to do a show for you. A down"n"under show. Crazy right? A new continent. What have I been up to? Well - I"ve been doing a bit to PlanMixPlay, and soon we might have some video.And when I say soon, I mean not soon, because I"m kind of a moron.If you"re still reading, you might as well tune in and listen, cause it"ll be way better than the lame jokes you"d find in this text.
